<TEXT>
<P>
The Israeli Defense Ministry said that Mordechai had a cordial
discussion with Kiyrikoghu on the past and future military
cooperations between the two sides, but gave no further details of
the discussion.
</P>
<P>
Kiyrikoghu arrived here Tuesday for a three-day visit as guest
of the Ground Corps Command of the Israel Defense Forces (IDF)
Major General Amos Malka.
</P>
<P>
During his stay, Kiyrikoghu was briefed by senior IDF officers
