1992. It has organized annual Walk-to-Guangzhou activities since
1994. Last year it organized a 2,850-kilometer Walk-to-Beijing
trip to mark the return of Hong Kong to China.
</P>
<P>
To date Sowers Action has funded more than 120 primary schools
in the Chinese inland, providing financing for the schooling of
more than 12,000 poverty-stricken children.  
