standard and stereotypical fashion of judging others negatively so
that the judge can be imaged to look like an innocent or a saint."
</P>
<P>
An official Information Sheet said that "the policy imposed on
Myanmar by the United States today is regarded as a precursor and
a catalyst to transform the process of a peaceful evolution into a
revolution by imposing sanctions, embargoes and pressures of all
sorts on our nation."
</P>
<P>
