have been hypocritically used as weapons while fabricated,
exaggerated and false news have also been constantly disseminated
to tarnish the image of the target countries," the Information
Sheet added.
</P>
<P>
In a report released last Friday, the U.S. State Department
slammed Myanmar's record of human rights.  
