time to beat Japanese wild card entrant Miho Saeki 6-2, 6-1.
</P>
<P>
The semi-final match against the Croatian Majoli will be their
first encounter since Hingis lost to her in the French Open final
in June, which prevented Hingis to monopolize all four Grand Slam
titles last season. 
