<HEADLINE> Haitian Minister to Inaugurate Embassy in Cuba </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HAVANA, February 5 (Xinhua) -- Haitian Foreign Affairs Minister
Fritz Longchamp started a three-day visit to Cuba Thursday to
inaugurate the embassy of his country in Havana.
</P>
