<HEADLINE> Chinese Association Helps Economic Development </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HEFEI, February 5 (Xinhua) -- The Association of Science and
Technology in Anhui Province, east China, has in recent years
served as a means of promoting local economic and technological
progress.
</P>
<P>
In the past five years, the association has signed 25,347
technological consultation contracts with local enterprises with
252.7 million yuan (31.8 million US dollars) involved.
</P>
<P>
An association official said that the cooperation between the
association and enterprises have helped local research institutes
put their hi-tech achievements to practical use.
</P>
<P>
At the same time, the association has set up a scientific and
technological information center to promote local economic
growth. So far the center has signed 7,068 technological
consultation contracts with local enterprises. 
</P>
